network-manager-l2tp (1.2.14-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * New upstream release.
  * Bump Standards-Version to 4.4.1
  * Set Rules-Requires-Root to no
  * Move D-Bus policy file to /usr/share/dbus-1/system.d/
